<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <title>Rejoindre l'Élite | Ambassadeur FORFEO LAB</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --gold: #d4af37; --blue: #007bff; }
        
        /* Effet de mouvement interactif */
        .stat-card {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: var(--blue);
        }

        .hero-amb {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #333 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
            border-radius: 0 0 50px 50px;
        }

        .vs-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">FORFEO <span class="text-primary">LAB</span></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navAmb">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navAmb">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto align-items-center">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/">Accueil</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3" href="/ambassadeur/details">L'Impact</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item ms-lg-3 mt-2 mt-lg-0">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill px-4 w-100" href="/login">Se Connecter</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero-amb text-center mb-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-3">Devenez un Expert de l'Ombre</h1>
            <p class="lead opacity-75 mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px;">
                Intégrez notre cercle restreint d'auditeurs mystères et aidez les établissements à atteindre l'excellence opérationnelle.
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 mb-5 text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card p-5 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <span class="vs-badge bg-danger text-white">SANS AUDIT</span>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">80%</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted small">des clients insatisfaits ne reviennent jamais sans rien dire.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card p-5 shadow-sm h-100 border-primary">
                    <span class="vs-badge bg-primary text-white">AVEC AMBASSADEUR</span>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-primary">+25%</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted small">de Chiffre d'Affaires moyen après correction du service.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="stat-card p-5 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <span class="vs-badge bg-success text-white">QUALITÉ</span>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-dark">4.9/5</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted small">Note Google moyenne visée par nos partenaires.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row justify-content-center pb-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 shadow-lg">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-center mb-4">Postuler au Cercle</h2>
                    <form action="/register" method="POST">
                        <input type="hidden" name="role" value="ambassadeur">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label fw-bold small">Nom Complet</label>
                            <input type="text" name="nom" class="form-control rounded-pill px-4" placeholder="Prénom Nom" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label fw-bold small">Ville de résidence</label>
                            <input type="text" name="ville" class="form-control rounded-pill px-4" placeholder="Ex: Paris, Lyon..." required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label fw-bold small">Email personnel</label>
                            <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control rounded-pill px-4" placeholder="votre@email.com" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label class="form-label fw-bold small">Mot de passe</label>
                            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control rounded-pill px-4" required>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 rounded-pill py-3 fw-bold shadow">ENVOYER MA CANDIDATURE</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
